-- Sharp May Build Second Overseas Solar-Cell Plant, Sankei Newspaper Says
-- Tak Kumakura
-- 2010-07-07T21:49:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/sharp-may-build-second-overseas-solar-cell-plant-sankei-newspaper-says.html

          
          
             Sharp Corp., which plans to build its
first overseas solar-cell factory in Italy, may also construct a
second factory elsewhere, the Sankei newspaper said, citing an
unidentified executive of the Japanese company.  
          
          


  


        